37
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,760
As we all know, the 500-meter is a short race. The starting speed is crucial.

38
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:17,060
Will Tang Xue maintain her position or will other athletes pass her?

39
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:21,960
