168
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:35,320
That's right! When I was coming in, I saw a club that was recruiting, so I signed up.

169
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:38,340
- You signed up? We'll be together. What club?
- Yeah.

170
00:15:38,340 --> 00:15:40,230
On-Ice Club.

171
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:45,120
Don't worry. I, Master Tang, will never leave you. I'll take you with me wherever I go.

172
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:49,920
A beautiful college life starts with joining a club.

173
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:08,510
My idol. I hope that one day I can be like you and be a world-class hockey athlete.

174
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:12,440
