00:19:39,050 --> 00:19:41,640
Lose five more teeth and you'll be more handsome than famous hockey star Brian Boyle.

228
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:44,670
You can even go play in the NHL.

229
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:47,880
I say, are you really okay?

230
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:51,770
